lead_paragraph: Devan Dubnyk has been one of the best goalies in the NHL lately. Good thing for the Minnesota Wild, too, because they haven't provided him with much offense.

headline.print_headline: Dubnyk Makes 15 Saves, Wild Beat Road-Weary Jets 3-1
